isRequired

private java.lang.Boolean isRequired()
Is the property required? That is, must the property not be null? This flag comes from the UML multiplicity lower bound; if it is less than or equal to 0, the property is not required, and if it is greater than 0, it is required. If there is no multiplicity specified, the property is not required.

Returns:
true if the property is required, false otherwise
